snippet.textDisplay: As a Chinese, I have visited almost most of our country. I would like to give you some recommendations. There are many beautiful snow mountains in Yunnan, such as Meili Snow Mountain and Jade Dragon Snow Mountain, as well as hiking holy places, Tiger Leaping Gorge, Antarctic Luo, etc., and I think which are more shocking than the city scenery. You are also welcome to go to Xinjiang or Tibet, which has the best scenery in China! welcome everyone to China!
